snippet.title: ONLY UP RISING - Chapter II
snippet.description:
Have you ever wanted to walk through the peaks and have an eagle vision? To fly over the world like a God ! 

*Available on Steam the first september ! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2565960/ONLY_UP__Rising/

Embark on an exciting journey in Only UP: Rising ! Play as a lost pirate on an island sheltering the ruins of a Lost City in the middle of the Pacific ! As you explore a huge world full of secrets and mysteries, you will have to climb as high as possible ! Cross an abandoned bazaar, haunted pyramids, Inca cities, ruins of the Great Wall, paradisiacal islands culminating at thousands of miles above sea level, a cemetery of planes! Try to reach the highest peak of this mysterious island.

• Song: "Epicness" by Anwar Amr
• Video Link: https://cutt.ly/ftqFyGA

#onlyup #videogames
